arameters().get(\"logUrl\"),\n            \"\",\n            \"\",\n            headers,\n            \"application/json\",\n            logEvent\n    );\n    executor.logger.info(\"DMaaP Response after sending LogEvent: \" + response);\n    return response;\n}"
